 is on the floor」 （地毯是在地上）… 「应该是前排旅客努力使用自己会的英文单词想要向这些‘只会英文的’乘务员拿毛毯，结果反被取笑。」该网友称。位于该网友前排的乘客在尝试用英文询问空乘如何填写入境卡时，同样得到了无比不耐烦的回答。空乘人员歧视非英语旅客？国泰航空：将严肃调查处理 _ 直击现场 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0e6525acf48d69e4d73fc2044d7fc460_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602475768"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIh+KO7bDu1JsIEAMaCDk2MTY0MDk0IIumrqMGMDM4qwhACnIJNjAyNDc1NzY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1684832885.274609", "card_id": "Q_597224718", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 132}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "雨天骑车上班被淋了，男朋友问我为啥不打伞，我生气发脾气了，男友因为我说他有病生气了，我真的很过分吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如下图。 请不要上升到人身攻击。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e6e5dcb66bb6c3407b9c5ee29c3d0ed3_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/597224718"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ih+KO7bDu1JsIEAMaCDk0OTk3MzMwILCFkqIGMBc4rAFAC3IJNTk3MjI0NzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1684832885.2755406", "card_id": "Q_601217984", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果刘备有「朋友圈」，会是什么样子的？"}, "excerp